---
title: No Chop Ginger Pork & Rice Skillet 3 easy steps to a delicious dinner
description: Our easiest-ever meals with no knifework and only one pan, done in a flash! You’ll sauté ground pork and broccoli with our speedy flavor MVP: aromatic garlic-ginger scallion paste. Serve it with quick-cooking rice, sprinkle with crushed peanuts, and dinner’s on the table in just 10 minutes with three steps, one pan, zero prep, and 100 percent deliciousness!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/67d7f83c18d6e477003fc909-01dd775d.jpeg
